'''Dugs-for-Democracy''' was an advocacy group during the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]], presumably formed by [[Dug/Legends|Dugs]]. It advocated Dug rights on [[Malastare/Legends|Malastare]] and opposed passage of the [[Military Creation Act/Legends|Military Creation Act]]. Its speaker was [[Toronaxx]].

